WEBVTT

00:11:59.360 --> 00:12:00.560
Remember Ingolf?

00:12:01.320 --> 00:12:05.416
Basically, I'm asking you
to find an Ingolf in your life,

00:12:05.440 --> 00:12:07.096
contact him or her

00:12:07.120 --> 00:12:09.600
and suggest that you can meet
for #dialoguecofee.

00:12:11.200 --> 00:12:14.656
When you start at #dialoguecoffee,
you have to remember this:

00:12:14.680 --> 00:12:19.776
first, don't give up
if the person refuses at first.

00:12:19.800 --> 00:12:23.800
Sometimes it's taken me nearly one year
to arrange a #dialoguecoffee meeting.

00:12:24.600 --> 00:12:25.856
Two:

00:12:25.880 --> 00:12:28.256
acknowledge the other person's courage.

00:12:28.280 --> 00:12:30.576
It isn't just you who's brave.